.Dd $Mdocdate: April 9 2018 $
.Dt OCTCRYPTO 4 octeon
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm octcrypto
.Nd OCTEON cryptographic unit
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "octcrypto0 at mainbus0"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver utilizes the OCTEON cryptographic unit to provide
a hardware-accelerated implementation of the following algorithms
for
.Xr ipsec 4 :
.Pp
.Bl -item -offset indent -compact
.It
AES-CBC
.It
AES-CTR
.It
AES-GCM
.It
AES-GMAC
.It
HMAC-MD5
.It
HMAC-SHA1
.It
HMAC-SHA2-256
.It
HMAC-SHA2-384
.It
HMAC-SHA2-512
.El
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr intro 4 ,
.Xr ipsec 4 ,
.Xr crypto 9
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
driver first appeared in
.Ox 6.4 .
